Hello everyone:innocent:
Glad to be a part of this community!

I am a Product Manager at <http://Admon.ai|Admon.ai> - an anti-fraud system for ads. I am looking for a marketer who worked with an anti-fraud system in the past or currently working with it. :dart:My goal is to share the product with the whole world, so we are preparing it for the different markets. It would be great if I'll be able to connect with 15-20 people to present the system and get feedback about it (UX/UI, additional details, features, etc.):gift: as a bonus, we can offer a free trial for a week if you wish to try it on your CPI traffic.

Ping me if you are able to share 20-30 mins for a quick call :pray:
